where on the last equality we have used the property $\sum_{j}\tilde{K}_j\prt{k;n,\gamma,\delta}x^{n-j}y^j=\prt{\gamma x+\delta y}^{n-k}\prt{x-y}^k$ derived in \cite{HuberEltschkaSiewertGuhne2018}. 

